bm.title: FusionExcel's Achievers Recognition Dinner MAEPS 04th July 2009 (1)

meta.description: FE's recent Achievers Recognition Dinner at MAEPS, Serdang, Malaysia on the 4th July 2009 was a GREAT SUCCESS with 1,800 Leaders, Members, VIPs and invited guests attending, many from overseas. The theme for the event was Country and Western with many FE members dressed up in their cowboy and cowgirl gear. Music and entertainment was provided by the 5 piece Country and Western Band, the Os Pombos. It was a fun night with great food, entertainment and fellowship among the Leaders and Members !
meta.author: klhunter
